01:15:05,716 --> 01:15:06,916
A fly.

782
01:15:11,187 --> 01:15:14,950
Have you read the papers?
See what happened?

783
01:15:15,200 --> 01:15:17,133
The government has fallen!

784
01:15:17,428 --> 01:15:18,878
All because of you!

785
01:15:22,964 --> 01:15:26,969
Commissioner, if it only takes
one fly to topple the government…

786
01:15:27,520 --> 01:15:29,006
Never mind.

787
01:15:29,905 --> 01:15:32,174
But keep yourself available!
- Alright.

788
01:15:32,397 --> 01:15:35,473
And don't leave the city! Let's go!
- Bye, Commissioner.

789
01:15:35,720 --> 01:15:37,692
Good day. Goodbye!

790
01:15:44,040 --> 01:15:46,037
Just stop it!

791
01:15:46,801 --> 01:15:49,531
I am tired! Therefore…

792
01:15:51,132 --> 01:15:53,213
you better watch yourself!

793
01:15:55,642 --> 01:15:59,070
Watch yourself.
Remember what happened to the fly!

794
01:15:59,160 --> 01:16:03,188
Because, you see,
even my patience has a limit.

795
01:16:03,278 --> 01:16:04,972
I can take it to a certain point,

796
01:16:05,062 --> 01:16:07,950
but I wind up uncontrolled,
then I become a hurricane!

797
01:16:08,040 --> 01:16:10,804
And then like nothing,
I sweep away dogs, cats,

798
01:16:10,894 --> 01:16:13,070
birds, fish and anything
that gets in my way!

799
01:16:13,160 --> 01:16:14,360
You got that?

800
01:16:16,440 --> 01:16:19,254
And I want to tell you
one more thing.

801
01:16:20,149 --> 01:16:23,239
You'll never win.
Never! Never! It's impossible!

802
01:16:23,549 --> 01:16:24,906
Because I am…

803
01:16:25,092 --> 01:16:26,596
I'm a man!

804
01:16:26,840 --> 01:16:28,878
Because I have a soul!

805
01:16:28,968 --> 01:16:32,377
I'm intelligent, cunning, crafty!

806
01:16:32,560 --> 01:16:35,109
Diabolical, if you want it!

807
01:16:36,021 --> 01:16:37,261
I'm a man!

808
01:16:37,351 --> 01:16:40,875
And an actor out of work
because of your persecution!

809
01:16:40,965 --> 01:16:43,895
Why did you do this to me?
I ask why? Why?

810
01:16:43,985 --> 01:16:46,773
Why? What do you want?
What are you?

811
01:16:46,930 --> 01:16:48,130
Who are you?

812
01:16:50,770 --> 01:16:52,726
You want to know? I'll tell you.

813
01:16:53,074 --> 01:16:57,029
You're nothing more than a bunch
of matter. Just nasty matter!

814
01:16:57,119 --> 01:17:01,077
Flesh and hair and nothing else!
You have nothing…

815
01:17:01,102 --> 01:17:04,731
You have no brain, intelligence,
spirit. You have nothing!

816
01:17:04,821 --> 01:17:07,376
I'll show you! Let me demonstrate!

817
01:17:13,414 --> 01:17:14,853
Here! Give me…

818
01:17:16,035 --> 01:17:17,947
Give me a little thought
about that grass.

819
01:17:18,037 --> 01:17:20,950
Go on, any whatsoever!
You can do it! Let's see!

820
01:17:21,173 --> 01:17:23,273
Let's see what you come up with.

821
01:17:24,840 --> 01:17:27,798
What are you doing?
Are you going to eat the grass?

822
01:17:29,063 --> 01:17:33,827
Come on, a simple little thought.
Even the most basic! Go on!

823
01:17:36,664 --> 01:17:40,440
See? You can't do it!
You have nothing in here!

824
01:17:40,530 --> 01:17:42,150
While I, my dear,

825
01:17:42,240 --> 01:17:44,688
if I want I can talk
to you about it for hours.

826
01:17:44,778 --> 01:17:47,152
With a blade of grass,
I can arrive at God!

827
01:17:47,242 --> 01:17:51,742
If I want, I can recite to you
100s, 1000s of verses on grass!

828
01:17:51,832 --> 01:17:56,221
Name me one animal that wrote
a single verse on the grass!

829
01:17:56,311 --> 01:17:57,661
They don't exist!

830
01:18:00,357 --> 01:18:03,404
You're… you're so ugly!
So primitive!

831
01:18:03,494 --> 01:18:05,567
What are you doing now? Huh?

832
01:18:06,539 --> 01:18:08,831
One moment! What does that mean?

833
01:18:11,202 --> 01:18:14,417
You think though you can't talk,
you can make yourself understood?

834
01:18:14,507 --> 01:18:17,555
But here's a newsflash, my friend,

835
01:18:17,800 --> 01:18:20,471
anything that you can do,

836
01:18:20,561 --> 01:18:24,092
I can do better!

837
01:18:26,377 --> 01:18:28,661
Remember that I'm an actor.

838
01:18:28,751 --> 01:18:33,254
My facial mobility and expressions
are practically unlimited!

839
01:18:33,344 --> 01:18:36,733
Go on, put me to the test
and I'll prove it! Don't be shy!

840
01:18:37,560 --> 01:18:40,132
Oh, no, you go first.
Please, begin.

841
01:18:46,332 --> 01:18:48,436
How is this? Lower lip!

842
01:18:52,539 --> 01:18:55,574
Combination. Combination x 3!

843
01:19:02,845 --> 01:19:05,873
Want to challenge me on agility?
Good!

844
01:19:08,342 --> 01:19:11,706
I'm up for it!
I said I'd accept any challenge.

845
01:19:42,306 --> 01:19:43,506
Animal!

846
01:19:43,805 --> 01:19:46,597
Animal! Disgusting!

847
01:19:46,856 --> 01:19:48,631
What are you doing? Spitting?

848
01:19:52,640 --> 01:19:56,419
You see the difference
between a man and an animal?

849
01:19:56,574 --> 01:19:58,449
Tell to whomever you report to:

850
01:19:58,539 --> 01:20:01,270
a man can do anything
and a beast nothing!

851
01:20:01,360 --> 01:20:05,271
And that's more…
more than just a difference!

852
01:20:05,440 --> 01:20:08,880
It…it…it's a wide abyss!

853
01:20:16,840 --> 01:20:19,719
Help!

854
01:20:25,936 --> 01:20:28,314
Help! Help!

855
01:20:28,404 --> 01:20:30,661
Help! Let me out!
- Where's the monkey?

856
01:20:30,751 --> 01:20:35,141
I don't know! We were arguing…
- Which way did he go?

857
01:20:35,231 --> 01:20:37,289
… he locked me inside
and ran away!

858
01:20:38,354 --> 01:20:42,507
And me? Let me out!
I don't want to stay here!

859
01:22:15,893 --> 01:22:17,093
Hey!

860
01:22:18,451 --> 01:22:19,651
Say…

861
01:22:20,183 --> 01:22:22,483
you see I'm no ape?

862
01:22:27,329 --> 01:22:30,443
Come on… What are you doing?
Be good, come now!

863
01:22:30,967 --> 01:22:32,767
Look at me very carefully.

864
01:22:33,023 --> 01:22:36,048
Tell me, can't you see?
I'm a man.

865
01:22:37,276 --> 01:22:38,746
Like the rest of you.

866
01:22:39,440 --> 01:22:42,886
I'm a man like your father.
Like your grandfather.

867
01:22:44,599 --> 01:22:45,956
A man.

868
01:22:46,355 --> 01:22:49,296
Cut it out! Stop… stop…

869
